.DT
set_login_mode
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
set_login_mode

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_login_mode -  This method sets the restriction level for loggin in.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int set_login_mode(int lvl)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^lvl%^RESET%^ - the restriction level
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 upon success, 0 upon failure
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/login_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the restriction level for loggin in.
This can be used to restrict access to the mud at three levels.
0 - unrestricted
1 - restricted to playtesters
2 - restricted to creators
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
query_login_mode()

.EP

